\pard\plain \fi360\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 The schooling in the Council-Controlled lands is two-part: primary and secondary education. In principle, every child should receive primary education. This is class-based, and happens mostly on the shard where the child lives, or nearby.}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 After primary education, the best children get sent to the capital for further education. This is more individually oriented, and focusses on training the child for a task in the Capital. Only a low percentage of children goes through this education.}}